# README
#

Shopping System

uses PHP, MySQL and Apache.

1. Create the database SHOPPING.
2. Create all the tables.
3. Create the database user.
4. The SQL code that does all the above is include @ db/shopping.sql.
5. Enjoy.

You can copy and paste the code on MySQL Command Line Client.
Please see README2.txt.
If you are using Apache, you can unzip the project into Apache web folder.
Point your browser to index.php. 
We are done. 
